{% block mainContent %}
  <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Roadmap</h1>
  <p class="govuk-body">Last updated: May 2024</p>

  <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What we're working on now</h2>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">GOV.UK One Login user activity history
    <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--blue">
      SIGNED IN EXPERIENCE
    </strong>
  </h3>
  <p class="govuk-body">Users will be able to view their GOV.UK One Login account activity history.</p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Users can prove their identity without photo ID
    <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--yellow">
      IDENTITY
    </strong>
  </h3>
  <p class="govuk-body">Users who cannot prove their identity with photo ID will be able to enter UK bank account details and their National Insurance number.</p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Users can keep their details up to date after proving their identity
    <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--yellow">
      IDENTITY
    </strong>
  </h3>
  <p class="govuk-body">Users will be able to make updates to their identity details (for example, their name) to keep their GOV.UK One Login up to date.</p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Maintaining trust in users who have already proved their identity
    <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--yellow">
      IDENTITY
    </strong>
  </h3>
  <p class="govuk-body">To maintain confidence levels over time, you’ll be able to repeat some identity checks for users who have already proved their identity.</p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">New data sources for security questions
    <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--yellow">
      IDENTITY
    </strong>
  </h3>
  <p class="govuk-body">New data sources and questions will be available for users proving their identity by answering security questions online (also known as knowledge-based verification questions).</p>

  <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--l govuk-section-break--visible">

  <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Recently released</h2>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">More configuration controls in the self-service admin tool
    <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--turquoise">
      SERVICE TEAM ONBOARDING
    </strong>
  </h3>
  <p class="govuk-body">Service teams can add and change an additional three configuration attributes in the self-service admin tool. This replaces the old route of having to contact a member of the GOV.UK One Login support team.</p>
  <p class="govuk-body">Also, admin tool users can now create and manage more than one service from the same account.</p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Two-factor authentication recovery
    <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--purple">
      SIGN IN
    </strong>
  </h3>
  <p class="govuk-body">If users lose access to their two-factor authentication method, we’ll help them get back into their GOV.UK One Login.</p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Users have other options to prove their identity if they’re not successful first time
    <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--yellow">
      IDENTITY
    </strong>
  </h3>
  <p class="govuk-body">Users who are not able to prove their identity the first time can try using another ID document or a different method.</p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Common navigation header for services connected to GOV.UK One Login
    <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--turquoise">
      SERVICE TEAM ONBOARDING
    </strong>
  </h3>
  <p class="govuk-body">Services using GOV.UK One Login will be able to use a common navigation header.</p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Use an international mobile phone number to create a GOV.UK One Login
     <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--purple">
       SIGN IN
     </strong>
   </h3>
     <p class="govuk-body">Users can create their GOV.UK One Login using an international mobile phone number.</p>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Services are shown in a user's GOV.UK One Login
    <strong class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--blue">
      SIGNED IN EXPERIENCE
    </strong>
  </h3>
  <p class="govuk-body">Users can see and access all the services they’ve used with their GOV.UK One Login.</p>

  <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--l govuk-section-break--visible">

  <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Updates</h2>
  <p class="govuk-body">As we’re still at an early stage, our plans may shift. We’ll update this page when this happens and add more detail when we can.</p>
  <p class="govuk-body">We’ll keep sharing in blog posts and at our regular cross-government show and tells too.</p>
  <p class="govuk-body"><a class="govuk-link" href="/mailing-list">Join our mailing list</a> to stay up to date.</p>
{% endblock %}
